        {
            "title": "歐聯｜阿仙奴兩回合9:3踢走燕豪芬 史達寧翻生兩助攻創紀錄：我仍可任重要角色",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"史達寧(左)貢獻2次助攻。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/615d7e49d1d92a16d7045ea70318bead/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031309385480482.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">史達寧(左)貢獻2次助攻。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>翼鋒史達寧今季由車路士外借阿仙奴後表現平平，上陣機會不多。不過，周三歐聯16強次回合，他踢出在槍手最佳一戰，交出2次助攻助球隊主場2:2賽和燕豪芬，兩回合計大勝9:3晉級，此子賽後即矢言自信仍可擔任重要角色。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"史達寧(紅衫)貢獻2次助攻。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c7de5bda94f3eb88a2fb375a6cdc0bca/2025-03/2025-03-12T214544Z_493915838_UP1EL3C1OG7M0_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-ARS-PSV-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        史達寧(紅衫)貢獻2次助攻。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"史達寧(紅衫)貢獻2次助攻。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b1e58e4db6db2d8065a0fc478062f484/2025-03/2025-03-12T211216Z_1610998965_UP1EL3C1MWEJX_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-ARS-PSV-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        史達寧(紅衫)貢獻2次助攻。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"史達寧(紅衫)貢獻2次助攻。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2fdd440e239fc29a6cb06b56549a3ecd/2025-03/2025-03-12T204542Z_629074735_UP1EL3C1LO4JD_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-ARS-PSV-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        史達寧(紅衫)貢獻2次助攻。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"史達寧(紅衫)貢獻2次助攻。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b4acf9f8b42bbd3d580fdcb801b39260/2025-03/2025-03-12T201002Z_1851277055_UP1EL3C1K0OGO_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-ARS-PSV-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        史達寧(紅衫)貢獻2次助攻。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴8強將鬥皇家馬德里。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/89a23ba9ed4e9c922cbe7371f2b4c1ef/2025-03/2025-03-12T204004Z_1636232003_UP1EL3C1LEQJ1_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-ARS-PSV-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴8強將鬥皇家馬德里。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴8強將鬥皇家馬德里。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/05d1af5e1628678fd09275695a055c06/2025-03/2025-03-12T203956Z_1434552481_UP1EL3C1LEJJ0_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-ARS-PSV-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴8強將鬥皇家馬德里。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴8強將鬥皇家馬德里。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/05d79437d431cafb87a3d3f126df7007/2025-03/2025-03-12T204114Z_240226649_UP1EL3C1LGPJ5_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-ARS-PSV-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴8強將鬥皇家馬德里。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴8強將鬥皇家馬德里。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/69667d2dbd73dd9305f64ece03e23b3c/2025-03/2025-03-12T201820Z_774982101_UP1EL3C1KEIHI_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-ARS-PSV-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴8強將鬥皇家馬德里。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴8強將鬥皇家馬德里。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/24f900517ef7ccfe66fcdd0bc7bba19b/2025-03/2025-03-12T215902Z_1902973499_UP1EL3C1P2CMI_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-ARS-PSV-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴8強將鬥皇家馬德里。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>阿仙奴9:3淘汰燕豪芬</h2>\n<p>開賽僅6分鐘，辛真高於禁區頂勁射破網為阿仙奴先開紀錄。12分鐘後，燕豪芬快速反擊，由比列錫禁區內射入追平。37分鐘，史達寧高速爆落底線傳中，迪格蘭賴斯頂入再度領先。完半場前，史達寧更有機會士哥，但單刀被救出。戰至70分鐘，客隊的迪奧治單刀笠入，最終雙方踢成2:2，兩回計槍手大勝9:3打入8強將鬥皇家馬德里。\n\n</p><h2>史達寧翻生兩助攻</h2>\n<p>史達寧今季外借至阿仙奴後都機會不多，今仗前於各賽事只上陣23場，當中僅9次正選上陣。今場難得正選他即踢得醒神，貢獻2次助攻，獲選為賽事MVP，並成為歐聯史上首位曾為4家不同球會炮製入球的英格蘭球員，這亦是他自去年11月後再參與入球。\n\n</p><h2>自信仍可任重要角色</h2>\n<p>史達寧賽後矢言：「很高興能夠上陣為球隊作出貢獻。我知道自己的能力。我只想上場比賽。在頂級球會與頂級球員在一起，只能等待機會，這是我正在做的事。」他續指：「我仍然堅信，我仍有很大的作用。我只能控制可以控制的事情。雖然我上場時間不多，但我有的是機會。我必須繼續努力，做好準備，盡可能幫助球隊。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057835/即時-體育-歐聯-阿仙奴兩回合9-3踢走燕豪芬-史達寧翻生兩助攻創紀錄-我仍可任重要角色",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-13 10:06:35",
